alerts.description:
There is a risk of gale-force gusts (level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 75-85 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 95 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: 50-60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations < 70 km/h

There is a risk of persistent rain (level 2 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 25-35 l/m²; in windward areas: < 45 l/m²

There is a risk of snowfall (level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Precipitation amounts: 10-20 cm

There is a risk of frost (level 1 of 2).
Height range: > 600 m; Minimum temperature: ~ -2 °C

There is a risk of light snowfall (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Precipitation amounts: 1-4 cm
